# CiberC-LG

SDK for Lighting Gale Cimcon that expose a client to platform.

## Use

```python
from lg import LGApi, LGAuth

...
lg_auth = LGAuth(username, password, base_url, ssl_verify=False, ...)
lg_api - LGApi(lg_auth)
...
```
